{"article_id":"wLe0da1X9Ujxevsu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump called the European Union a \" foe \" of the United States in an interview","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"which aired Sunday ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"just one day before his controversial","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"- and still unexplained -","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"meeting with Russian president Vladimir Putin in Finland .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Asked to name America ' s \" biggest foe globally right now \" during an appearance on CBS ' s Face the Nation ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"the first answer","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that came to Trump ' s mind","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"was the E.U .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" Well I think","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"we have a lot of foes -","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the European Union is a foe -","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"what they do to us in trade .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Now , you wouldn ' t think of the European Union ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"but they ' re a foe , \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Trump replied .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"He then added","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that \" Russia is a foe in certain respects , \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and that China was one economically ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"though he insisted","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that he wasn ' t judging the countries to be \" bad , \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"but just meant","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that they were \" competitive . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"When asked to identify his `` biggest foe globally right now , ''","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"President Trump told @ jeffglor","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the European Union is a \" foe \" of the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The president also said","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Russia is a \" foe in certain respects \"","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and China is a `` foe economically. \"","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"https : //t.co/Npe9S4uLuh","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"pic.twitter.com/oHDpY4HrK2 - CBS News","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"( @ CBSNews )","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"July 15 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Trump ' s remarks follow an escalating pattern of often haphazard attacks on America ' s European allies , especially in recent months","depth":3},{"id":35,"text":"as Trump ' s attempts","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"to start a global trade war","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"have intensified .","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Last week at a NATO summit in Brussels , Trump launched a fresh attack on Germany ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"claiming","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"the country was \" totally controlled \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and held \" captive by Russia \"","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"thanks to a gas pipeline deal","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"which the president grossly misrepresented the importance of to Germany ' s energy needs .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"He also criticized America ' s NATO partners","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"for not upping their military spending faster","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"than they had already agreed to ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"only to later up the ante","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"and tell them","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"they would need to spend more of their GDP on defense","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"- 4 percent -","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"than even the U.S. does .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Then ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"before making his first state visit to the U.K. ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"the president gave a crazy interview to a British tabloid","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"in which he blasted British prime minister Theresa May","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and praised her primary rival ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"criticizing her handling of the Brexit crisis","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"- though he later tried to deny having made the","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"( recorded )","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"statement .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"A few days after that diplomatic disaster , May subsequently revealed","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that Trump had advised her to sue the E.U .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"instead of negotiating with them over Brexit ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"indicating that Trump continues to exclusively view foreign policy through the narrow lens of real estate industry bullying .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Another frame for Trump ' s criticism of Europe was white nationalism ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"as he also said last week","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that it was a shame that European countries were allowing their cultures to be erased","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"by allowing in immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"When Face the Nation ' s Jeff Glor told Trump","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that \" a lot of people might be surprised to hear","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"you list the E.U . as a foe before China and Russia , \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Trump made it sound","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"as though it upset him to have to challenge Europe , his ancestral homeland .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"\" No I look at them all -","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"look ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"E.U . is very difficult , \"","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" I want to tell you .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Maybe the thing","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that is most difficult -","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"don ' t forget","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"both my parents were born in E.U . sectors","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"okay ?","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"I mean","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"my mother was Scotland ,","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"my father was Germany .","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"And , you know","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"I love those countries . \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Trump went on to repeat last week ' s attacks on Germany and America ' s NATO allies ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"and he repeated his backhanded compliment","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that he respects how E.U . leaders have been able to taken advantage of the U.S .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Considering Trump ' s statements about other world leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"he seems to afford much more praise and respect to more authoritarian leaders","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"than most European countries have to offer .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"In the same Face the Nation interview , Trump claimed","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that he had \" low expectations \" for his Monday meeting with one such leader , Vladimir Putin .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Asked to explain","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"why he was meeting with Putin at all ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"he would share that","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"after the meeting was over -","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"a non- answer","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"which may mean","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"he didn ' t know what to say .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"it ' s a good thing to meet","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"I do believe in meetings , \"","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Trump also offered what appeared to be a response to the considerable anxiety","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"over what he might agree to , give away , or improperly disclose during a private meeting with Putin , an ex-KGB agent","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"who has already gotten Trump to publicly repeat Russian propaganda .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"\" Nothing bad is going to come out of it , \"","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Trump promised .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":148,"right":228,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":119,"right":147,"relation":"organizati